# Force LF everywhere so checkouts are byte-identical across OSes. Windows runners default to
# core.autocrlf=true, which would rewrite files to CRLF on checkout and break the Biome format
# gate (and any byte-sensitive golden test) before a single test runs.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never end-of-line converted.
*.png binary
*.webp binary
